# Test / local IO
# ====================
tests_io/inputs/*
!tests_io/inputs/.gitkeep

# 如果 tests_io/outputs 是人工确认过的 golden files，就不要忽略。
# 如果 tests_io/outputs 只是本地运行产物，再打开下面两行：
# tests_io/outputs/*
# !tests_io/outputs/.gitkeep

